author: The Linux Foundation
description:
🚀 The Linux Foundation Research team is launching its 2025 research agenda! We're diving into open source AI, cybersecurity, open data, skills training, and more. 📊

These studies shape the future of open source—tracking trends, identifying challenges, and uncovering new opportunities. Want to be part of it? Become a sponsor and help shape the insights or participate in surveys to make your voice heard!

📩 Get involved: research@linuxfoundation.org
